Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.23,0:00:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.77,0:00:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.88,0:00:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.09,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.89,0:00:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.17,0:01:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.61,0:01:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.92,0:01:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.18,0:01:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十九話\N[戰場的英雄]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團的支配制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.56,0:01:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遍及全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它所到之處都發生糾紛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.73,0:01:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本國也主張和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.33,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制止胡亂的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.53,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸入他的支配下\N的確能得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.24,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那根本不是真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是壓制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.97,0:02:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓制又會產生新的糾紛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的行動有成績嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在歷史裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上有許多國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,許多民族和許多思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生若干糾紛\N或許是無可避免的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由是賜予所有人的權力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.80,0:02:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.53,0:02:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全自由不被認同也是必須的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.10,0:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平共處須要的關懷別人的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不是戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從過去學習\N創造正確的新未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為反抗羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有本國是做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，山克王國這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是已故匹斯克拉福特國王提倡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平義生根的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們強大的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是遵從我父王的教誨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我十分明白\N我這種人的言行很失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，為了令更多的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更多的人能得到真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.21,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我請求各位協助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順利結束了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.09,0:03:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們並非在監視各位的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.56,0:03:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來比原定快了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們意見一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才不必花太多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，被討厭的人也告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是眼中釘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.24,0:03:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們並非討厭羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.35,0:03:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是希望她快點糾正錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.32,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在許多生命消失之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.70,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯爵，宇宙服有兩件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.30,0:04:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降下的看來果然只有那兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.10,0:04:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，看來也不用戒備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.74,0:04:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙衛星和羅姆斐拉財團結盟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的任務已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有命令要處死鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處死他們很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本國也歸入\N羅姆斐拉財團的支配下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.72,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想擱置他們的處決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，你討厭動物嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜歡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，和牠們玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠們看來比較喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.76,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動物本能地知道誰是仁慈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭須要那種仁慈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不須要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥不須要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N戰鬥以外的時間就須要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是戰鬥時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本應有命令要處死我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好總部有聯絡來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們親自前來接收鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.73,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不用親手殺死你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我實在很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.94,0:06:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，到時我同樣要交出你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能再麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.91,0:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你照指示做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們打算束手就擒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時候未到還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們沒打算白白送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們好堅強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對本國參加羅姆斐拉財團的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配政策抱有疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但為了避免無益的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只好選擇這條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.30,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是保護許多生命正確決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的宇宙也做了相同的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們對羅姆斐拉財團來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是個障礙\N但只有這樣..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才有存在意義的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來取自己性命的人是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想死的就只有戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我們能做的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.42,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要做的只有那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不想死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運輸機聽好，馬上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們奉命擊落你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆，馬上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北緯50度，很冷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.54,0:07:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不可以乖乖交給OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉‧普奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要感謝我們幫妳取暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新OZ是個仁慈的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是確認運輸機裡有甚麼之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是重要的客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我聽說\N只要鋼彈的駕駛員行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和他們有關的叛亂份子就會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.68,0:08:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但想不到能得到鋼彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的駕駛員果然回到地球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無論如何要把那東西\N交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,參加羅姆斐拉財團的國家\N急速增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後不會輕易成功呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鋼彈的就不會有金屬反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有運輸機的金屬反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剔除那反應   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?   敵襲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉在海底的是真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我或許會說謊騙妳救我出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了對抗羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們和相同的敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.54,0:09:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快決定是否進行交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連決定的時間也沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，敵人的集結也很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ稱為01的機體啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，妳說想鋼彈幫助妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的國家在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不能說，我只能告訴妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是個因為反抗羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不知何時會被攻擊的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.99,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後的時代需要的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.09,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在統治那國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人能為這世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶來真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳認為只靠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能打贏羅姆斐拉財團?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.91,0:10:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定能粉碎羅姆斐拉的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都認識鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那令我們經常魯莽行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為倚靠他們會有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在，我想要他們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也不想有戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有能力戰鬥的人就應該戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是那樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然說甚麼正義是大言不慚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那些孩子配得起那字眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.21,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實那或許是可悲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他們迫作為時代的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想追隨他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.51,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為那樣會令我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用走上錯誤的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅鋼彈的作戰\N在兩處地方進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一處是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.24,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一處\N是希洛你留下的鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被稱為01的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你認識山克王國嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在羅姆斐拉財團的機密資料裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她被記錄為問題國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克…王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.56,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有巧妙地掩飾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們非常嚴密的監視著01
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有它的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去幫助他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,監視我們的只有這兩隻狗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是叫我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家不希望有戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是戰鬥的火種呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡的司令官也有弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧，卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.01,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機影正接近這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦辛特伯爵有聯絡來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上確認吧   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.65,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們朝羅姆斐拉的部隊去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們為何不逃走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那部隊的緊急來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我們聯絡接近中的飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦辛特柏爵，這是他們留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈駕駛員給我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯爵，說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[希望你馬上報告我們逃亡了]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.74,0:13:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[我們不可以再為你們添麻煩]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.57,0:13:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我們逃走就行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃去哪裡也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.61,0:13:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲!敵襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客氣了!去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現敵人!魚雷發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然魯莽，但只有這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道很魯莽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舉手!反抗是無用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.55,0:15:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你們也聯絡其他戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.25,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不想再增加傷亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照他說話做比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是我，我馬上就會攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其實希望你不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那種事不可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，今後去哪裡好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.28,0:15:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有想去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球有很多仁慈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果我們去他們那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.59,0:15:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就會令他們有麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經無處可去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，因為你想忘記戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要地球是戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.40,0:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，你也只好戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.87,0:16:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只容許活在戰場上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰鬥中活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.05,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我們的生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莎莉，這邊成功鎮壓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.96,0:16:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳那邊如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們正在久別重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳用它幫助妳的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，多謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫路克蕾琪亞‧諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我效力的國家叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵，不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使不知道妳的國家的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會相信妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能協助反抗羅姆斐拉的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.61,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經覺得很光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去搜索其他鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若得到有關情報\N妳再來支援我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有兩三個駕駛員就信心培增呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了令妳也相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.13,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向神和本國的名字發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.36,0:17:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,監視和平國家的人正要回去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.07,0:17:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特地趕來的我真像個傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為利用這機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.38,0:17:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進攻山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，靠MD一定不足夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那種木偶沒理由敵得過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護公主殿下的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日來的轉校生沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽聞\N那和羅姆斐拉財團中心人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪爾麥優侯爵有血緣關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然妳會責備我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為是討厭山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.57,0:18:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平主義的某財團的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只是相學習山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建設和平國家的教育方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.32,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以派留學生轉校來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.82,0:18:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能相信財團的一切言行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懷疑別人不會有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我們無愧於心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為也是一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能令他們明白那一點的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是本學園的理事長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道山克王國的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.88,0:19:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也兼任學園的理事長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲‧卡塔羅尼亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好尊敬妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一個人仍然甚麼也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在一起學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父王提倡的完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如妳所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.27,0:19:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是從羅姆斐拉財團來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,財團現在於這個戰亂之世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有大量武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.28,0:19:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對山克王國的方針\N非常有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那些人攻來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道妳會怎樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.75,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種美麗的風景\N會在一瞬間消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.12,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到那種事，連心也會被迷住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也不想眼白白看著這國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被那種野蠻的笨蛋催毀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候，妳會怎樣做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為這個世上沒有笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對話就能互相了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.11,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信那會給予所有人和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.38,0:20:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡戰爭，好喜歡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.32,0:20:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這種人在這個國家是障礙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，山克王國的首要目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.52,0:20:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是成為能這樣子討論的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.33,0:20:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後也時常討論吧\N桃樂絲小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.73,0:20:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳叫我桃樂絲就行\N莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳也叫我莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下是時代的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.01,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為莉莉娜殿下妳是我的偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲‧卡塔樂尼亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和莉莉娜殿下相同年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於她是獨立行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是被羅姆斐拉支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.83,0:20:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我暫時還未清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.26,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不能太意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別放鬆監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.57,0:20:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也準備了這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.87,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但桃樂絲小姐看來很難應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲小姐看來非常喜歡戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.91,0:21:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在莉莉娜殿下\N想否定戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信她的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.15,0:21:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會令莉莉娜殿下很疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下的想法非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.66,0:21:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是明知不適合這時代的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.69,0:21:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護那樣的莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使拿起武器也好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以讓莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這國家\N被暗殺的國王一樣遇害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.74,0:21:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們正在面對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.17,0:21:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不可以重覆的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使使用任何卑鄙手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要保護莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要成為這國家的影子活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.01,0:22:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點爆發戰爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.76,0:22:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.76,0:22:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.76,0:22:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.76,0:23:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.26,0:23:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.76,0:23:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.76,0:23:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.29,0:23:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團的勢力不斷擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.53,0:23:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界各地氣勢如虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.19,0:23:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛成為反抗的特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.90,0:23:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某部隊的僱庸兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.97,0:23:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨意地參加了戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾對戰鬥會解決一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱有疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.14,0:23:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時的卡特爾得知了抵抗財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.34,0:23:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主張完全和平主義的國家的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.94,0:23:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第三十話
